39:25.420 --> 39:27.300
And they're saying, hey, let's test

39:27.300 --> 39:31.180
AlexNet and other similar deep nets since then

39:31.180 --> 39:34.420
on a more realistic, harder version of object recognition

39:34.420 --> 39:37.060
that's more characteristic of what humans do.

39:37.060 --> 39:40.700
And so they're generating this huge data set of stimuli

39:40.700 --> 39:42.260
that they crowdsource.

39:42.260 --> 39:43.980
And so people, workers on Mechanical Turk,

39:43.980 --> 39:45.740
