Well, the way to dig in is to start

01:15:13.240 --> 01:15:17.040
by saying, what question is being asked in this paper?

01:15:17.040 --> 01:15:18.800
If the paper is well written, you'll

01:15:18.800 --> 01:15:22.680
be able to find that in the abstract, blah, blah, blah,

01:15:22.680 --> 01:15:24.440
to study the effect of face inversion

01:15:24.440 --> 01:15:26.240
on the human fusiform face area.

01:15:26.240 --> 01:15:27.720
