01:15:27.720 --> 01:15:29.560
But if you fish through the abstract,

01:15:29.560 --> 01:15:31.440
you should be able to find what question is being asked,

01:15:31.440 --> 01:15:35.280
and it's the first thing you should figure out about a paper.

01:15:35.280 --> 01:15:37.600
You don't necessarily read a paper,

01:15:37.600 --> 01:15:39.080
start beginning through the end.

